name: Hamster Island Demo
description: This is a beautiful paradise for small hamsters. Let\'s build a village for the cute little hamsters! You can build buildings such as farmland, cafes, and restaurants for hamsters. Invite new hamsters to join this community. There are also funny hamsters dressed up as other animals waiting for you to discover! Come and play with the cute hamsters in Hamster Village!
